Vienna To-Do File
=================

Update this file with a list of things that users have requested but which aren't yet implemented.
Thanks!

Accepted for 2.2
================
- Single article list and viewer interface (as in Bloglines).

Known Issues (May not be fixed)
===============================
- Renaming a folder does not update the folder name in smart folders that reference it.
- The isAccessible(NSString * urlString) function returns NO behind a firewall.
- A SQLite databases cannot be written to on remote folders. Vienna will warn and prompt for an alternative location.

Wishlist
========
- Bloglines integration.
- Show the feed icon in the article list pane/unified view.
- Support retrieving and posting Atom/RSS 2.0 comments.
- Spotlight support.
- Change dock unread count colour and size.
- Bonjour support.
- Selection count in status area.
- Absolute or relative date and time of last (and/or next?) refresh in status area.
- Handle middle mouse click on tabs.
- Hide and show article pane.
- Timestamp on each row in the activity log window.
- Applescript: extend article object to allow writing as well as reading properties.
- More options in date field in smart folders: last 24 hour, last 24-48 hours.
- Detect duplicate articles in separate folders and show only once.
- Show "New..." commands on folder popup menu.
- Cache full XML for original article and return via Applescript.
- Show warning icon on collapsed group folder if any sub-folders have warnings.
- Mix conditionals within smart folders.
- Show article count for folders (including Trash).
- Empty Trash command in contextual menu for Trash.
- Per-feed refresh settings.
- Unread count for smart folders.
- Synchronisation via .Mac or FTP.
- Fix web browser to block popups.
- Download images within articles so that they can be viewed offline.
- Next Unread command moves to next unread article rather than next feed in unified layout.
- In unified view, different styles for read and unread articles.
- Preference UI for setting # of simultaneous refreshes.
- Individual layout, view, sort, and filter settings for folders.
- Choose location of new subscriptions (in sheet?).
- Growl notifications for individual feeds.
- Enable flagging of articles in unified view (with contextual menu?).
- Preference to expire unread articles as well as read articles.
- Check for internet connection before checking for new articles.
- Hold down option key (or other combo) while pressing mark all read button to mark all subscriptions read.
- Use shift key to toggle whether to open tabs in foreground/background in Vienna.
- Drop-down navigation list for back and forward buttons in browser pane.
- Drop-down overflow list when too many tabs are open.
- When deleting subscription, also delete smart folder rules involving that subscription.
- Add CSS variables for localizable strings.

Rejected Requests
=================
- Support for AmphetaRate (http://amphetarate.newsfairy.com/index.php). [Server is offline - no replacement known].
- Ad-blocking for HTML view. (http://braden.machacking.net/). [Server not found].

